item.title: 【Live Audios (lossy)】MP3 - TAYLOR SWIFT: THE ERAS TOUR LIVE (FILM AUDIO) (EDIT)
item.description:
Hey! Here's the thing: I've made myself a The Eras Tour Live Audio to listen to it on my own, but then I thought that I could share it with you guys so you could have fun with me also, so here is "Taylor Swift: The Eras Tour Live (Film Audio)" Big thanks to @ArDa3851 's theard of "Taylor Swift: The Eras Tour (2023) HDCAM (No Crowd Noise Version)" for the high quality of footage and sound that made me decide to make an MP3 version of this.

(https://sharemania.us/threads/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-2023-hdcam-no-crowd-noise-version.230617/)

Other than that, I also edited something on this too, such as cutting out the speech and the silence between each song (that was too long) to make it faster, and I also made seamless transitions to it (I tried my best) so you guys could listen and have fun with these smoothly.

The list of things that I cut out between songs (so you could prepare):

- "The Man" Speech
- "Champagne Problems" Speech
- "Tolerate It" Piano Intro
- "All Too Well" Speech
- "Betty" Speech
- "All Too Well" Speech
- "Our Song" Speech
- "Midnights" Intro
